---
title: Sticky Honey-Soy Chicken & Fried Rice with Asian Greens
description: This dish has a little bit of everything, including an array of colour. It’s a tasty rainbow! From the sweet, honey-soy soaked chicken to the nutritious veggies tucked into the fried rice (there’s even egg in there too), we know everyone will be pleased.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64ab56da57da307c4116c7f6-189f37c8.jpeg
